item.title: Untitled Novel: Ch. 1: Failed Initialization
item.description: The first chapter (excluding the prologue) of my free to read & distribute amateur novel. I’ll probably share the next few chapters in my Blog’s RSS feed, but if you’re interested in reading you can find a link to the dedicated RSS feed to follow it specifically.
